Thirteen equals one

单词和词组：
vicar 牧师
for one cause or another 因为这个或那个
with a start 受到惊讶或惊醒
armed with a torch 装备了一个手电筒
catch sight of 看见
grocer 杂货商

好句：
woke up with a start:... 由于受到惊醒。冒号后面是一个解释性的分句
recognize as 认出是
whatever are you donging up here?你究竟在这上面干什么？whatever用于加强语气
You certainly did give me a surprise!助动词do放在谓语动词之前用来表示强调
Thirtteen is not as good as one, but it is better than nothing。

